                        "content": "The nurse is caring for a client diagnosed with polycystic kidney disease. The nurse collects the following client data: blood pressure is 144/92 mm Hg; the client is complaining of 5/10 bilateral flank pain; the client is voiding pink-tinged urine; and the client’s urine output was 75 milliliters over the last 3 hours. Which of the collected assessment data would prompt the nurse to contact the nephrologist?",
